OL,3,CTwo men jailed for a combined total of
OL,4,C24 years after machete attack
OL,6,FTwo men have been jailed for a
OL,7,Fcombined total of more than 24 years
OL,8,Fafter a man was almost killed in
OL,9,FBasingstoke.
OL,11,FAmman Majid, 18, of Chivers Close,
OL,12,FBasingstoke, and Charlie Costen, 21,
OL,13,Fof Harlech Close, Basingstoke,
OL,14,Fattacked a man on the footbridge on
OL,15,FBuckskin Lane, near Grampian Way.
OL,17,FThe man, in his 40s, was chased by a
OL,18,Fgroup of young men on electric bikes
OL,19,Fduring the incident, which took place
OL,20,Fat around 11pm on Tuesday 30 January.
