OL,3,CTwo men jailed for a combined total of
OL,4,C24 years after machete attack
OL,6,FWinchester Crown Court heard the man
OL,7,Fhad just purchased drugs and was later
OL,8,Fthreatened by the group.
OL,10,FHe was then attacked with a machete
OL,11,Fand was taken to Basingstoke and North
OL,12,FHampshire Hospital with serious facial
OL,13,Fand head injuries.
OL,15,FDetectives launched an investigation
OL,16,Fand arrested four people. Majid and
OL,17,FCosten were both charged with
OL,18,Fattempted murder.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
