OL,3,CTwo men jailed for a combined total of
OL,4,C24 years after machete attack
OL,6,FMajid was found guilty of attempted
OL,7,Fmurder and possession of a bladed
OL,8,Farticle and was jailed for a total of
OL,9,F19 and a half years at Winchester
OL,10,FCrown Court.
OL,12,FCosten was cleared of attempted murder
OL,13,Fbut was found guilty of wounding with
OL,14,Fintent. He was jailed for a total of
OL,15,Ffive years.
OL,17,FDC Rowan McComb, CID North, said:
OL,18,F"This was a shocking incident and it
OL,19,Fis miraculous that the victim of this
OL,20,Fsenseless and violent attack did not
OL,21,Flose his life.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
