OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F413A1733855553
OL,3,CTwo men jailed for a combined total of
OL,4,C24 years after machete attack
OL,6,F"I would like to thank the victim of
OL,7,Fthis needless attack for the bravery
OL,8,Fand courage he has shown throughout
OL,9,Fthe investigation and trial.
OL,11,F"This assisted us in putting two
OL,12,Fdangerous young men behind bars. I
OL,13,Fhope this outcome will encourage any
OL,14,Ffuture victims to put their trust in
OL,15,Fthe police and assist us in the
OL,16,Fcontinued issues we face with drug-
OL,17,Frelated violence.
OL,19,F"We will continue to do all we can
OL,20,Fensure to ensure that those who carry
OL,21,Fknives will be put before the courts.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
