OL,3,CTwo men jailed for a combined total of
OL,4,C24 years after machete attack
OL,6,F"I would also like to thank my
OL,7,Fcolleagues, whose dedication and hard
OL,8,Fwork throughout this complex
OL,9,Finvestigation ensured we could present
OL,10,Fa thorough pack of evidence ahead of
OL,11,Fthe trial."
OL,13,FChief Inspector Hayley O'Grady,
OL,14,FBasingstoke's District Commander,
OL,15,Fadded: "We know this incident had a
OL,16,Fhuge impact on the local community,
OL,17,Fhowever I want to reassure you that
OL,18,Four officers take reports of knife
OL,19,Fcrime in the district extremely
OL,20,Fseriously.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
