OL,6,F"In the days and weeks after this
OL,7,Fincident, our officers carried out a
OL,8,Fnumber of reassurance patrols and made
OL,9,Fenquiries in the Buckskin and South
OL,10,FHam area.
OL,12,F"Our commitment to tackling knife
OL,13,Fcrime continues and we are dedicated
OL,14,Fto working with partners and
OL,15,Forganisations to engage with young
OL,16,Fpeople about the dangers of knife
OL,17,Fcrime and help divert them away from
OL,18,Fserious violence.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
