OL,6,F"I hope this case sends a strong
OL,7,Fmessage to anyone who chooses to carry
OL,8,Fa weapon or become involved in serious
OL,9,Fviolence, no good ever comes from it.
OL,10,FThe consequences destroy lives
OL,11,Fforever."
